comment:
* Specification of time range for read and delete requests. Internally represents a SQLLite
 * argument that specifies start and end time to put in as SQLLite parameters. The filter must be
 * bound at least at one of the ends, i.e., either the start or end time must be set, or else an
 * IllegalArgumentException is thrown.

methods.name: public Instant getStartTime()
methods.comment: * @return start time instant of this filter

methods.name: public Instant getEndTime()
methods.comment: * @return end time instant of this filter

methods.name: public boolean isBounded()
methods.comment: * @return a boolean value indicating if the filter is bound or not.
